title: 2019 Week 10 Preview
itunes:title: 2019 Week 10 Preview
description:
A room filled with heroes - Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler, Chris Wesseling and Gregg Rosenthal preview each of the upcoming games of week 10. A few big anticipated matchups include Panthers Packers (6:15), Bills Browns with the muscle man, Nick Shook, on the phone (11:11) and Rams Steelers (28:47).

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
